    "Question Answering (QA) For the QA type (Figure 4), fine-tuned models generate more generic responses than models adapted with incontext learning.",
    "Instead, fine-tuning results in fewer hallucinated responses for Llama2 C, al-though it has no effect for Mistral I.",
